{"code":0,"data":[{"cid":11723,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Alice","permissions":["report"],"pid":2175,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"唯一的问题是早上环境比较亮而且比较吵影响睡眠质量","timestamp":1592800855,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":11735,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Bob","permissions":["report"],"pid":2175,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"你现在熬的每一次夜，都会成为压垮后来你的一根稻草\n当然不熬夜是不可能不熬夜的【滑稽】","timestamp":1592800890,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":11743,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Carol","permissions":["report"],"pid":2175,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"亲身体验，熬夜胃会不舒服，早起不会","timestamp":1592800929,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":11772,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Dave","permissions":["report"],"pid":2175,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"没有。睡眠的关键是“规律”和“睡够”。如果你每天都熬夜，并且起的晚，睡眠时间充足，睡眠质量好，就没问题。早上环境比较亮可以拉窗帘嘛。","timestamp":1592801087,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":11779,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Dave","permissions":["report"],"pid":2175,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"“亲身体验”是不足以成为证据的，不能确定因果关系，也不能确定是个体差异还是普遍规律。","timestamp":1592801127,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":11812,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Eve","permissions":["report"],"pid":2175,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"难道自己感受不到皮肤显著变差么（","timestamp":1592801277,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":11850,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Francis","permissions":["report"],"pid":2175,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"真的，熬夜伤身","timestamp":1592801427,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":11885,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Dave","permissions":["report"],"pid":2175,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"为什么你清还会有这么多科学素养不佳的人。。","timestamp":1592801574,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":11887,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Dave","permissions":["report"],"pid":2175,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"（上一条指某些回复）","timestamp":1592801585,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":11932,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Grace","permissions":["report"],"pid":2175,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"晚睡晚起和早睡早起本质上都是可以的，只要保证作息规律性（相关文献查得到的吧","timestamp":1592801764,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":12048,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Hans","permissions":["report"],"pid":2175,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"上个月试验了一下，白天拉窗帘晚上开灯，上午八点睡下午四点起，持续两周感觉良好（但是晚上没有什么外卖吃","timestamp":1592802365,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":12168,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Isabella","permissions":["report"],"pid":2175,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"重点在于规律作息和规律饮食～","timestamp":1592803154,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":12937,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Jason","permissions":["report"],"pid":2175,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"经常白天睡晚上或者半夜才起，感觉比白天起更有活力","timestamp":1592808521,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":12943,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Kate","permissions":["report"],"pid":2175,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"丁香医生有篇文章 只要睡够没任何影响","timestamp":1592808558,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":14288,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Eve","permissions":["report"],"pid":2175,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"我之前一直2点睡，11点起，这睡眠时间够长了吧，皮肤就是变差了啊。讲再多科学道理，最终不是作用到个体么？而且哪家的科学研究是100%确定的呢？没想到你清还有科学素养这么“高”的人啊","timestamp":1592817292,"type":"text","url":""}],"post":{"attention":false,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"likenum":3,"permissions":["report","fold"],"pid":2175,"reply":15,"tag":null,"text":"请教一下，如果睡眠时间一定，熬夜真的比早起危害大吗？有什么科学依据吗？","timestamp":1592800728,"type":"text","updated_at":1606782583,"url":"","vote":{}}}